---
title: Apricot Ponzu Chicken with Ginger Lime Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: Tonight’s chicken is all about the swoon-worthy pan sauce that’s made with apricot jam, citrusy ponzu, garlic, ginger, and butter. On the side, there’s jasmine rice and roasted broccoli. (Pssst—those sides would be equally delicious with the sauce.) This is one full meal we’re pretty sure you’ll want to whip up around the cluck.
